OL,3,CD-Day 80 The Last Veterans: Ron Hendrey
OL,5,FRonald Hendrey, Age 99, Royal Navy
OL,7,FInterviewed 2 November 2024
OL,9,FAn able seaman and gun loader on board
OL,10,Fthe destroyer HMS Ulster on D-Day, Mr
OL,11,FHendrey and crew had sailed into the
OL,12,FEnglish Channel under cover of
OL,13,Fdarkness the night before.
OL,15,FUlster had been deployed in the
OL,16,FMediterranean in the Summer of 1944
OL,17,Fbut had been called back to undergo
OL,18,Ftraining exercises in the English
OL,19,FChannel ahead of the landings.
