OL,3,CD-Day 80 The Last Veterans: Ron Hendrey
OL,5,FIt was given the task of escorting a
OL,6,Fconvoy of ships across the Channel and
OL,7,Fjoining the bombardment of German
OL,8,Fdefences off the section of shore
OL,9,Fknown as Gold Beach ahead of the
OL,10,Flandings.
OL,12,FThe crew had only been told what was
OL,13,Fhappening a short while before they
OL,14,Fset off.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/7
