OL,3,CD-Day 80 The Last Veterans: Ron Hendrey
OL,5,FMr Hendrey said: "After a while it
OL,6,Fsettles down, what he said settles
OL,7,Fdown and your nerves disappear. It
OL,8,Fdoes take a moment when you're being
OL,9,Ftold you're going into action and a
OL,10,Fmajor action at that. One minute and
OL,11,Fit's settled down and it's like you're
OL,12,Fgoing into training again.
OL,14,F"If you look at the destroyer, there's
OL,15,Ffour guns on it, two before the bridge
OL,16,Fand two in the quarter deck. And that
OL,17,Fwas the main armament.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/7
