OL,3,CD-Day 80 The Last Veterans: Ron Hendrey
OL,5,F"Well I was on the one just underneath
OL,6,Fthe bridge. It was called B gun deck
OL,7,Fand I was a cordite loader and that
OL,8,Fwas supplied from the ammunition
OL,9,Flockers.
OL,11,F"And I would load the cordite after
OL,12,Fthe shell had gone and the captain of
OL,13,Fthe gun would shut the breach."
OL,15,FUlster stopped about half a mile off
OL,16,Fthe French shore and began firing.
