OL,3,CD-Day 80 The Last Veterans: Ron Hendrey
OL,5,FMr Hendrey added: "We were escorting
OL,6,Fthe troops. That was our job to escort
OL,7,Fthem in. The boats they were on had no
OL,8,Farmament. So the destroyer would be
OL,9,Ftheir armament. We didn't land of
OL,10,Fcourse the Royal Navy. We just had
OL,11,Fspecial areas to blast.
OL,13,F"There was no willy nilly firing. Each
OL,14,Fship had a section and our section was
OL,15,FKing section, and that was where we
OL,16,Fhad a blast off.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/7
