OL,3,CD-Day 80 The Last Veterans: Ron Hendrey
OL,5,F"What sticks in my mind is the amount
OL,6,Fof aircraft that went over. The sky
OL,7,Fwas black with them. I assume they
OL,8,Fwere paratroopers but where they
OL,9,Flanded heaven knows."
